Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.90,0:02:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄 欢迎归来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出迎场面很大 方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.90,0:02:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄 志志雄 志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.08,0:02:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三十九话\N制造逆刃刀的人\N新井赤空最后的一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.45,0:02:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一回到京都就觉得很安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村 往这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.79,0:02:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维新至今十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.46,0:02:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在日本全国四处游走\N唯有这个地方没有再来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.67,0:02:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕府末期的动乱\N没有一天不充满血腥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.41,0:02:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛地狱图画般打斗的战场\N就在这京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.51,0:02:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发什么呆啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看！到家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葵屋餐厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,餐厅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.69,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 在京都小有名气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.27,0:03:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比以前回来得迟些  害我担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 因为发生许多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.81,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.68,0:03:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛…痛死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来晚了处罚你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 欢迎归来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.88,0:03:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎归来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长高了 长高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.36,0:03:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没谢谢你 休息一下再走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.26,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是绯村拔刀斋 ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.23,0:03:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算十字刀疤隐藏起来\N知道的人还是知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.67,0:03:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到里面再详谈 请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.91,0:03:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先去洗个澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.41,0:04:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.22,0:04:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在道上没说自己是\N“隐密御庭番众”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.70,0:04:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如你所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.87,0:04:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柏崎念至以前是\N御庭番众成员之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名为京都探索员“阿翁”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.04,0:04:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开这间葵屋是做为京都聚点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.48,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江户幕府总店先倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过维新后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.68,0:04:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就变成那些没事做的同志\N他们暂时的落脚处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还满有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以苍紫才把小操寄在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识苍紫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.80,0:04:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该先跟你说才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.94,0:05:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样\N般若们死了而苍紫行踪不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.14,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你暂时要对小操保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.72,0:05:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村你十年不曾出现在京都\N现在来难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.82,0:05:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的接班人\N志志雄真实有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.30,0:05:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我锻练有素\N京都内外的事我大概都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.14,0:05:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耳中传入他在京都造反之事\N我简直不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.01,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连你也现身了我不得不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.31,0:05:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好不好？\N我强力的支持你做你后盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.85,0:05:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢现在的京都\N有人要破坏的话绝不饶他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.79,0:05:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护京都\N老兵要再度出征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 啊啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这间葵屋没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家以前都是隐密御庭番众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.81,0:06:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起保护小操\N都是可信任的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.04,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不要也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是养大小操的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了你也不听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就我不客气拜托你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.13,0:06:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想请你帮我找人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新井赤空和比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.23,0:06:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能快点找到这两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起床了绯村 天亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.95,0:06:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经起来了啊\N本想看看你睡眼惺忪的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦…小操 你穿那样是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是京都的家居服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.02,0:07:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说穿着忍者服\N在老家走来走去有点那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿翁 这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.80,0:07:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿翁老先生早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要找的人里面\N其中一个有消息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.47,0:07:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 正确的说\N应该是知道他已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.21,0:07:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制造逆刃刀的刀匠\N新井赤空在八年前已经作古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.45,0:07:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刀匠…对了\N要打一把替代折断的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.12,0:07:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那位刀匠已经死了\N就不会有第二把逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.56,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过还有希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.06,0:07:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤空把所有的技术\N传给他儿子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要现在就去看看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.30,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我白天出去会有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.44,0:07:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对手是志志雄\N你怎么躲藏终究会被发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.71,0:07:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿翁老先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村你不是为了本国的人民\N而和志志雄战斗的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.45,0:08:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以正大光明的去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.49,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是正直男人的作风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？说得不错吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看爷爷这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.76,0:08:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前还被推举为\N隐密御庭番众最有力接班人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.84,0:08:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他说\N今后是年轻人活跃的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.44,0:08:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推荐苍紫做接班人\N自已反倒屈居做京都探索员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.24,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新井赤空\N幕府末期有名的刀匠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.18,0:08:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,致力于探究斩人刀、杀人刀等\N被刀匠界视为异类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.56,0:08:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探究杀人刀的刀匠\N制造出不杀人的逆刃刀来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.60,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人的人生\N有时会让人觉得矛盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.33,0:08:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对？绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.54,0:08:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤空的儿子新井青空\N继承担任刀匠的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在是明治时代\N刀剑不受重视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.41,0:09:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前以是打制菜刀\N镰刀等的生活用具维生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定\N他可以制造出新的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.99,0:09:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问新井青空在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.12,0:09:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦…青空？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在 窝搜 窝搜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？窝搜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,窝搜 窝搜 窝搜 窝搜\N不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握手\N窝搜 窝搜 窝搜 窝搜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要握手啊 好乖好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.07,0:09:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊织 不可以顽皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.51,0:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.74,0:09:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 需要什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想买一把菜刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以试切看看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…  又黏起来 回复原状了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,复原刀法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.97,0:10:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到\N切口组织完全没有破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.61,0:10:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切下去又回复原状了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.91,0:10:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名刀结合高手的技术\N是高难度的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.65,0:10:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简单的菜刀就能做到\N不愧是赤空的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了 就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.59,0:10:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的逆刃刀\N就决定给新井青空制造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.02,0:10:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘 可以让我见青空吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.00,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要请青空打造一把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公  爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们好 我是新井青空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.47,0:10:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是青空？怎么不太像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那边去再聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.82,0:10:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至于一定要我来打刀一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.92,0:10:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我已经不打刀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们去找别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.33,0:11:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道家父赤空\N探究杀人刀一事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.67,0:11:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家父在幕府末期时常说\N我打造的刀创造出新时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.51,0:11:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家父凭此信念制造出的刀\N夺走许多人的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.95,0:11:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人怎么是创造新时代\N我无法认同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  伊织！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.03,0:11:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在是明治\N和平时代终于降临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武士们放下刀剑\N所以我一样也不做刀匠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.51,0:11:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定只做生活用具\N过和平的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.78,0:11:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你和你父亲相反\N拥护和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么主义的我是不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.72,0:12:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢和平\N我想任何人都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.09,0:12:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天真 你太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么和平的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.70,0:12:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想颠覆这和平时代的人\N真真实实的还活在世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青空 非常抱歉\N提出了无理的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逆刃刀要怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.24,0:12:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是不杀人的逆刃刀\N却也是打斗的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在不忍心叫那样的人来做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.42,0:12:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重头再来寻找逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.69,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位剑客…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.86,0:12:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什么理由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不帮他打造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.33,0:12:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就把父亲留下的\N最后一把刀让给它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 这样就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.34,0:12:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样和平的明治\N已经不需要刀剑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定是拔刀斋  赶紧报告志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.12,0:13:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天真 太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的长像\N还有说话的样子都很软弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.72,0:13:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,施加压力的话绝对行得通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.32,0:13:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青空的和平生活\N我不能自私的去搅乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.06,0:13:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勉强叫他做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.17,0:13:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有刀匠的真心\N只会是件差劲的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法跟折断逆刃刀的宗次郎\N或是志志雄打斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村就死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.38,0:13:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有形体的逆刃刀一无是处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.45,0:13:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的逆刃刀\N必须要超越断掉的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.79,0:13:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么教出少根筋的女儿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在京都的刀匠里寻找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？认输了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞苦无！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握手 握手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.81,0:13:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青空要是替我打造逆刃刀\N志志雄一定不会放过他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.64,0:14:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想把和平过日的一家人\N牵连进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葵屋也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.85,0:14:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是以前御庭番众的成员\N也不可能平安无事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到下个刀匠前\N必须离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方治 交待你的事办好了没？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.74,0:14:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预定要的火药都买好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄\N你不是和宗次郎在一起吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.92,0:14:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要他负责\N去把东日本的十本刀找来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.86,0:14:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都像安慈那样不好找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.09,0:14:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西日本这边\N我直接吩咐下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.37,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十本刀集结之后就开始国变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吧！ 同志们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,群起暴动的时刻来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.68,0:15:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各自的准备先做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.15,0:15:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.15,0:15:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄 志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄 志志雄…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.26,0:15:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上去联络全国的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话还没说完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十本刀全部集合好\N要花不少时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然大家都已经充满了杀机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.37,0:15:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为庆祝国变\N先让十本刀拿拔刀斋来血祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.78,0:15:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄 要三思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.01,0:15:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十本刀\N是担任重要任务的特攻部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.52,0:15:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿来对付拔刀斋 \N万一伤到他们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我也吓一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.66,0:15:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N十本刀没有那么脆弱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.69,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 由美姐说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.26,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的十本刀\N不会输给拔刀斋一个人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说大话 猎刀张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在大阪住一阵子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.67,0:16:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正想展露一下\N最近得到的爱刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.38,0:16:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这个臭剑客刚好可以杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.82,0:16:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经吸了好几个人的血\N你们看这把刀耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.02,0:16:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是美的让人目不转睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.19,0:16:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是这样\N一讲到刀剑的事眼睛就亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.60,0:16:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方治 拔刀斋有什么动向？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.24,0:16:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没掌握他的行踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.37,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只知道日前他和\N新井赤空的儿子青空接触过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.18,0:16:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻求替代被宗次郎弄碎的\N那把逆刃刀吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青空拒绝替他打造新刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.62,0:16:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤空留下的最后一把刀\N并没有交给拔刀斋 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕府末期的名刀匠\N新井赤空留下的最后一把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正事当前你不要乱来坏事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管绯村和爷爷怎么说\N不赶紧拿到新刀的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜咕噜咕噜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀！扫把 扫把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扫把？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是说我的头发吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小孩真好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.73,0:17:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友 你爸爸呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 需要什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有赤空的最后一把刀吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家父的最后一把刀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 偶然听人谈到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.91,0:17:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名刀匠新井赤空的最后一把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以借看一下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这人是从哪里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.32,0:18:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家父的刀现今全都下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我手边一把也没留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？大概是我听错了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.57,0:18:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.30,0:18:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢刀剑\N一心想要耍不同风格的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才会当上剑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.17,0:18:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.74,0:18:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.01,0:18:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.12,0:18:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.52,0:18:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊织！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.73,0:18:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.24,0:18:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？这叫逆中空纳刀\N没几个剑客会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.07,0:19:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的没有最后的一把刀\N太震惊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.78,0:19:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,许许多多的刀里面\N我最喜欢赤空的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.42,0:19:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太震惊了\N好像手又想挥第二次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.16,0:19:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样的工夫\N我从来不人前表演第二次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.86,0:19:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们有眼福了\N好好看着吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有家父的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.47,0:19:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后一把刀已经奉为御神刀\N献给白山神社了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然真的有嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们真坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.75,0:19:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事不宜迟 我马上去拜见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们太坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.42,0:19:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在还不确定你说的\N是真还是假之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小孩借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在那里别动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会乱来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:20:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要是吵闹的话\N小孩会变怎样我不敢保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.08,0:20:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对那老哥再施点压力\N拜托他一定要打造逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.94,0:20:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要告诉他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.08,0:20:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一把刀被称做作御神刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.75,0:20:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸的刀里面\N唯一没有染上血腥的一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连那把都沾上血腥的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.59,0:20:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸就不是真正的刀匠\N只不过制造杀人道具的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.73,0:20:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个时候不说的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.50,0:20:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的名誉固然重要\N现在却是伊织的命比较…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.37,0:20:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道没有看那男人的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是喜欢刀剑的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.31,0:20:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是喜欢拿刀杀人的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.64,0:20:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拿到爸爸的刀之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.75,0:20:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不拿手边的东西来试刀\N是不会善罢甘休的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.02,0:20:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.25,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不再打造刀剑了\N为什么还会变成这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.89,0:20:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是刚刚那位…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我详细状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.03,0:20:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.03,0:21:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多快说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.07,0:21:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小操 你回京都来了啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.67,0:21:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有急事要通知爷爷  准备一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.18,0:21:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从婆婆那儿来的信鸽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要传达情报给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.46,0:21:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是小操传来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.60,0:21:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青空的儿子\N被志志雄的人强带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.17,0:21:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.54,0:21:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的逆刃刀断了不能用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.77,0:21:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了也不能尽力发挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.81,0:21:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能去报仇的 绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.85,0:21:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.82,0:22:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤空的最后一把刀\N到底是怎样的杀人刀呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.84,0:22:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.07,0:22:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是来神社参拜的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.44,0:22:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.98,0:22:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把小孩放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.95,0:22:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十字刀疤…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.08,0:22:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你就是\N有名的杀人拔刀斋 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.42,0:22:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是来拿赤空的\N最后一把刀吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.66,0:22:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧！谁敢来阻止我\N我就杀了他
